==English==

===Adverb===
{{en-adv|head=[[before]] [[dark]]|-}}

# Before [[night]] begins to fall. From [[morning]] until [[evening]]. In the daytime before sunset.
#: ''I think you should finish mowing the lawn '''before dark'''.''

